 is concluded that CH+ is a good FUV tracer\nin star-forming regions. The effect of potential X-ray irradiation is not\nexcluded, but cannot be demonstrated by the present data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2013 12:31:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
